=== Nupidya ===
Ɣ umzwaru, Wikipidya iga ansmad i usnfar Nupidya. Wad iggʷran iga yan usnfar n tgrumsna igan fabur ɣ ifili illan s [[Tutlayt Tanglizt|tnglizit]], imgradn nns da tn ttaran imuzayn. Nupidya ittusnflul ɣ 9 maṛṣ 2000 ddu tilit n Bumis, yan waggur wantirnit.

